From Kristoffer Eriksson Subject Re Science and methodology was Homeopathy tradition In article quqlgINN Russell Turpin writes My definition is this Science is the investigation of the empirical that avoids mistakes in reasoning and methodology discovered from previous work Reading this definition, I wonder when should you recognize something as being a mistake It seems to me, that proponents of pseudo sciences might have their own ideas of what constitutes a mistake and which discoveries of such previous mistakes they accept Kristoffer Eriksson, Peridot Konsult AB, Stallgatan , S Oerebro, Sweden Phone e mail Fax or mail swip net kullmar pkmab ske